  (str title) (str `Page 3`)
  (str content) (str `3
SCHEDULE
FORM NO. 1.
Form No. 1.
N OTICE is hereby given by the Collector of Land - revenue in Bombay, under Act XI. of 1853, that
( describe the encroachment ) is to be removed or abated within one month from the date hereof; otherwise
the same will be removed or abated by the said Collector under the authority of the said Act.Dated
the day of in the year of our Lord
( Signature of Collector. )
_________
Form No. 2.
This W arrant, granted by the Collector of Lan d - revenue in Bombay, under Act XI. of 1853, is to
authorize of to remove ( describe encroachment ).
Dated ( Signature of Collector.)
———`)
  (str footnotes) (str )
  (str sourcePage) (int 3)
